org.jamsim.io

Interface ParameterSet

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    WeightCalculator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CategoricalVarAdjustment, CategoricalVarWeightCalc, ContinuousVarAdjustment

    public interface ParameterSet
    A set of parameters. The parameters are represented by a TableModel.
    Version:
    $Revision$
    Author:
    Oliver Mannion

    • Method Detail

      • resetDefaults

        void resetDefaults()
        Reset the parameters to their default values. Will usually need to be followed by validateAndNotify().

      • validateAndNotify

        void validateAndNotify()
                       throws InvalidDataException
        Process a change to the parameter set (ie: the underlying TableModel). Validates the values then notifies all Observers that there has been a change. External methods should call this after making any changes to the underlying TableModel.
        Throws:
        InvalidDataException - if the underlying TableModel values are invalid
